code standard

class(module, bundle and etc.) name: capitalize first letter, connect words with '_'

wire/reg name: capitalize first letter of every word(camel)

io name: connect words with '_', no capital letter

abbreviation: follow universal rules like ID, SoC or FIFO, DO NOT FOLLOW RULES ABOVE

module structure:

1.statement( including io)

2.io connection

3.reg&submodule connection(update)

4.wire connection